     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "YoungProjector[shape, content] returns the matrix of the Young subgroup \
projector, namely, the projector over the Young subgroup associated with \
content in the irreducible representation of the symmetric group associated \
with shape. YoungProjector[shape] represents an operator form of \
YoungProjector to be applied to a content. YoungProjector[shape, rep] \
represents an operator form and uses the array rep of matrices of adjacent \
transpositions in the symmetric group.", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, 
